# 📄 `deployment.yaml` (8080 version)

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: speed-api
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: speed-api
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: speed-api
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: speed-api
          image: speed-api:1.0
          imagePullPolicy: Never
          ports:
            - containerPort: 8080
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: speed-api-service
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: speed-api
  ports:
    - name: http
      port: 8080
      targetPort: 8080
      nodePort: 30080
```

